			<name>
				<baseName xml:lang="en">Oil and gas reservoir evaluation | Three types of pre-exploration zones | Resource value calculation </baseName>
				<baseName xml:lang="zh">油气藏评价| 三类预探区带| 资源价值计算</baseName>
			</name>
			<classificationInformation>
				<common:classification>
					<common:class level="0">Materials production</common:class>
					<common:class level="1">Other mineralic materials</common:class>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">According to the templates and parameters of the pre-exploration zones, the strategic value of resources in five pre-exploration zones in Sichuan Basin is evaluated. In order to facilitate comparison and comparison, we normalized the evaluation index according to the exploration status of the pre-exploration zone in Sichuan Basin </common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">根据预探区带的模板及参数对四川盆地的 5 个预 探区带的资源战略价值进行评价。为了便于比较和对比，我们根据四川盆地预探区带的勘探现状进行了评价指数的归一化</common:generalComment>
		</dataSetInformation>
