			</locationOfOperationSupplyOrProduction>
		</geography>
		<technology>
			<technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses xml:lang="zh">基于勘探风险 分析技术建立了“油气发现概率 － 资源战略价值”的预探区带评价模板，提出了对应的评价参数、赋值标准、计算公式及结果分类标准，实现了统一平台下的预探区带评价优选。</technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses>
			<technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses xml:lang="en">Based on the exploration risk analysis technology, the pre-exploration zone evaluation template of &quot;oil and gas discovery probability-resource strategic value&quot; is established, and the corresponding evaluation parameters, assignment standards, calculation formulas and result classification standards are put forward, thus realizing the evaluation and optimization of pre-exploration zones under a unified platform.         </technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses>
			<referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture type="source data set" refObjectId="937a3075-865a-f2ca-50dc-f4c543dfffdb" uri="../sources/937a3075-865a-f2ca-50dc-f4c543dfffdb.xml">
